---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <main>
    <div>
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">About me</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        I am a Full Stack Developer with an interest in cutting-edge technology!
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Currently, I'm a professional full stack web developer, but I write blog
        posts about all sorts of tech in my own time. I also work on some
        personal projects to learn new things.
      </p><p class="mb-4">
        Here are some facts about me:
        <ul>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2">🌍</span>Based in Rotterdam, The Netherlands.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2">🎓</span>BSc in Information Technology from the
            Rotterdam University of Applied Sciences
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2">💼</span>Professionally working with TypeScript
            and Angular.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2">🦀</span>Currently learning the Rust programming
            language.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2">📚</span>Check out my technical blog on
            <a href="https://mbvissers.medium.com" target="_blank">Medium!</a>
          </li>
          <li><span class="mr-2">🤓</span> Besides programming, I like to snowboard, read fiction books, and play video games like any other nerd.</li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2">📌</span>Check out my <a
              href="https://github.com/mbvissers"
              target="_blank">GitHub</a
            > profile to see some of my work!
          </li>
        </ul>
      </p>
      This website is open source. Check the <a
        href="https://github.com/mbvissers/portfolio"
        target="_blank">repository</a
      >!
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  @reference "../styles/global.css";

  li {
    @apply mb-4 ml-2;
  }
</style>
